snippet.title: I made a horror game about school
snippet.description:
After 3 Months I finally decided to show a sign of life again by releasing a Horror Game about school.
If I remember right, I wasn't drunk while making this game... and this kinda botheres me...

If you want to support a Guy who makes Games and likes Capybaras (that's me) consider:
⭐ Subscribing 🔔(Else Mrs. Chalk will stab you with her bare hands)
Protect your dog from Mrs. Chalk🏫: https://capybaraforge.itch.io/ring-academy
Making a gingerdead man🎄:https://capybaraforge.itch.io/gingerd...
Helping Sophia with the laundry🦝:https://capybaraforge.itch.io/racoonf...
Checking out Mr. Lupin 🎩: https://capybaraforge.itch.io/mr-lupin
Visiting my First Game's page🐶: https://capybaraforge.itch.io/three-m...
Or following my Itch.io account so you don't miss my next Horror Game 🦺🥽 : https://capybaraforge.itch.io/

In 'Ring Academy', you'll embark on a surreal journey as the newest student at a school like no other. Your path to navigating this bizarre institution involves throwing rings to progress through levels, each more whimsical and eerie than the last. Prepare for the strangest classes you've ever attended, taught by eccentric teachers who are anything but normal.
